name: The Nymph of La Ferla Manor
description:
One of the three maidens of La Ferla Manor. The Nymph is playful and lonely, frolicking around her home in solitude.

Shot on location at the home of Dominic La Ferla in Torrance, California.

See the body painting in motion at: https://youtu.be/A1VawigwYxI

model: Shadia Elise Ghantous
body paint and photography by: Roustan (bodypainter.com)
